    <div class="header"><div class="doc-title">GENERAL INFORMED CONSENT & RIGHTS</div></div>

    <div class="section-title">1. CONSENT FOR ADMISSION & GENERAL TREATMENT</div>
    <div style="border:1px solid #000; padding:10px; font-size:11px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        I, the undersigned, hereby give my consent for the admission and treatment of the patient named __________________________.
        I authorize the doctors and staff of Sewa Sadan Hospital to administer necessary medical treatment, nursing care, and diagnostic tests (X-ray, Labs, etc.).
        <br><br>
        I understand that the practice of medicine is not an exact science and NO GUARANTEE has been made to me regarding the outcome of the treatment.
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">2. FINANCIAL RESPONSIBILITY</div>
    <div style="border:1px solid #000; padding:10px; font-size:11px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        I agree to settle all hospital bills as per the hospital's tariff. I understand that interim bills must be cleared within 24 hours of presentation.
        If paying via Insurance/TPA, I understand that any disallowed amount is my responsibility.
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">3. PATIENT & FAMILY RIGHTS (ACKNOWLEDGEMENT)</div>
    <div style="border:1px solid #000; padding:10px; font-size:11px;">
        I acknowledge that the Patient Rights and Responsibilities have been explained to me in a language I understand.
        <ul>
            <li>Right to respectful care and privacy.</li>
            <li>Right to information about diagnosis and costs.</li>
            <li>Right to refuse treatment.</li>
            <li>Right to complain/give feedback.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

